revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Add categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata -->
== Usage ==
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
{{Wikibooks inline|Wikisource work}}
</syntaxhighlight>
This template creates an inline link to Wikibooks in list format.

== Examples ==
; Normal:<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{Wikibooks inline|Work}}</syntaxhighlight>
:{{Wikibooks inline|Work}}

; Full link override:<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">{{Wikibooks inline|links=[[b:Foo|]] and [[b:Bar|]]}}</syntaxhighlight>
:{{Wikibooks inline|links=[[b:Foo|Foo]] and [[b:Bar|Bar]]}}

; List format:<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext">
 {{Wikibooks inline|list=
 * [[b:Foo|]]
 * [[b:Bar|]]
 }}
</syntaxhighlight>
:{{Wikibooks inline|list=
* [[b:Foo|Foo]]
* [[b:Bar|Bar]]
}}

==See also==
{{Commons templates see also}}
* {{lts|Wikibooks}}
* [[Template:Wikibooks redirect]]
* {{lts|Cookbook}}
* [[Wikipedia:Wikimedia sister projects#Wikibooks]]

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line; interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Inline interwiki link templates]]
[[Category:Wikibooks link templates]]
}}</includeonly>

